                    breach of this Agreement.  This is in addition to any other rights and remedies the applicant or Company may have.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The Committee Member acknowledges that such use or disclosure of Confidential and Proprietary Information as described in the “Non­Disclosure Agreement” may constitute insider trading in violation of federal law, resulting in sanctions on individuals   and the corporate entities involved in insider trading.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div id="articleV">
                <h3>ARTICLE V. CONFLICTS OF INTEREST AND RELATED ACTIVITIES</h3>
                <p>
                    By execution of this agreement, the Committee Member certifies that to the best of his/her knowledge and belief,
                    no conflict of interest, real or apparent, professional, financial, or personal, as set forth in the “Conflict of
                    Interest Policy for CPRIT Scientific Research and Prevention Program (SRPP) Committee Members,” which the
                    Committee Member will sign, and is incorporated herein by reference, exists in relation to performance under
