                </p>
                <p>
                    The Committee Member acknowledges that he/she remains under a continuing obligation to comply with the
                    conflict of interest policy and that the Committee Member will promptly disclose any conflicts of interest and
                    follow the recusal process established by CPRIT.
                </p>
                <p>
