                    For purposes of this restriction, "professional
                    services" do not include those services for which an honorarium is paid;
                    however, honoraria exceeding $5,000 shall be reported within 30 days to CPRIT.
                </p>
                <p>
                    While performing work as a Committee Member under this agreement,
                    the Committee Member may not serve as a member of the board of directors or
                    other governing board of a CPRIT grant recipient that is currently receiving CPRIT grant funds.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div id="articleVI">
